m/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Maxim-of-The-Prodigy.-Credit-Paul-Bergen-min-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Maxim-of-The-Prodigy.-Credit-Paul-Bergen-min-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Maxim-of-The-Prodigy.-Credit-Paul-Bergen-min-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Maxim-of-The-Prodigy.-Credit-Paul-Bergen-min-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-prodigy">奇才乐队</a>宣布，自基思·弗林特去世以来，他们的首场美国头条秀将于旧金山举行。</p><p>这场演出将于 4 月 14 日在旧金山 The Warfield 举行，这将是他们自 2017 年以来在美国的首场头条演出。</p><p>旧金山演出将在 The Prodigy 前往美国参加科切拉音乐节期间举行，音乐会定于加州音乐节后的第一个周末举行。这也将是乐队自<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/prodigy-keith-flint-cause-of-death-inquest-2460047">2019 年 Keith Flint 去世</a>以来的首场演出。</p><p> “我们很高兴再次在美国进行现场演出，”这支电子乐队在 Instagram 的标题中宣布了这一消息。 “我们一直很喜欢在那里表演。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DE5U_2tt-WD/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" v